r av sitt levebr\u00f8d hos Trondheims dominerende drosjeselskap."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c3b238914f15418630843420eb160a8d20451b54d0efc1b220fb643ae31e519f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-06-18T18:16:46.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Med krefter og kompetanse forent i et felles selskap skal fem st\u00f8rre norske drosje-selskaper bli mer effektive. Tr\u00f8nderTaxi eier 19,6 prosent av Taxus Norge AS."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1221112.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Taxi-SMS.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/6cfb0606068db0931fe213936731dd01a70b6597.jpg?5996b1ba"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "1500 biler i taxi-allianse -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "6cfb0606068db0931fe213936731dd01a70b6597"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "business"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["taxus norge as", "netcom"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["selskapet", "biler", "samarbeid", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["bergen taxi", "sarpsborg taxisentral", "trondheim og malvik", "taxus norge", "drammen taxi og fredrikstad", "fr\u00f8ya og r\u00f8ros", "trondheims", "drammen taxi", "tr\u00f8ndertaxi 330", "taxus", "taxi akershus", "taxus akershus"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["lysaker", "kl\u00e6bu", "b\u00e6rum", "\u00e5fjord", "agdenes"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field":